{
  "id": "platform-at-scale",
  "name": "Platform at Scale",
  "briefing": "You now run 8 models in production. The fraud model needs to retrain every hour as attack patterns change. The recommendation model trains on 2TB of interaction data — current CPU training takes too long. The churn model's predictions degraded last month: data drift went undetected for 3 weeks.",
